--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following is a list of the major customizations
made to the lua-5.1.4 sources for BZFlag.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Renamed Makefile to Makefile.orig, and  (svn r18913)
   src/Makefile to src/Makefile.org

2. Added Makefile.am  (svn r18913)

3. Applied the lua_pushhstring patch  (svn r18916)

4. Applied the LUA_CALLINSINDEX patch  (svn r18917)

5. Added lua_setuserdataextra() and lua_getuserdataextra() for
   faster userdata type checking  (svn r19238)

6. Renamed the source files from .c to .cxx for g++ compilation  (svn r19274)

7. Applied the __usedindex metamethod patch  (svn r19401)

8. Added the __rawset metamethod  (svn r19402)

9. Added the lpeg library  (svn r19430)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
